Welcome, Immortal.

You have the keys now. Don't waste them.

Basic Commands:

  goto <room>        - Travel to any room by VNum
  transfer <name>    - Bring a player to your location
  shutdown           - Bring down the server gracefully
  purge              - Clean up corpses and loose objects
  oload <vnum>       - Create an object
  mload <vnum>       - Create a mobile
  zreset             - Reset a zone
  stat <target>      - View detailed info on mob, obj, or player
  where              - See all players and their locations
  wiznet <message>   - Broadcast to all immortals
  force <name> <cmd> - Force a player to execute a command
  slay <name>        - Instantly kill a player or mob
  restore <name>     - Fully heal a player
  vnum <type>        - Search for mobs/objs/rooms by VNum

Rules:

  - Do not spawn items for player characters without verification.
  - Invisible does not mean anonymous. Players can tell.
  - Use 'nohassle' to keep mobs off you while working.
  - Use 'holylight' to see in dark rooms.
  - If unsure, ask a higher-level immortal or read the help files.

The world is in your hands. Don't break it.
